#, no-wrap
msgid "Pre-commit hook {#pre-commit-hook}"
msgstr "Enlace de acuerdo previo {#pre-commit-hook}"

#. type: Plain text
#: site/content/en/dev.md
msgid ""
"You can automatically run `reuse lint` on every commit as a pre-commit hook "
"for Git. This uses [pre-commit](https://pre-commit.com/). Once you [have it "
"installed](https://pre-commit.com/#install), add this to the `.pre-commit-"
"config.yaml` in your repository:"
msgstr ""
"Puede ejecutar automáticamente `reuse lint` en cada confirmación como un "
"enlace previo a la confirmación para Git. Esto usa [precommit](https://pre-"
"commit.com/). Una vez que [lo haya instalado] (https://pre-commit.com/"
"#install), agregue esto a `.pre-commit-config.yaml` en su repositorio:"

#. type: Fenced code block (yaml)
#: site/content/en/dev.md
#, fuzzy, no-wrap
#| msgid ""
#| "repos:\n"
#| "-   repo: https://github.com/fsfe/reuse-tool\n"
#| "    rev: v1.0.0\n"
#| "    hooks:\n"
#| "    - id: reuse\n"
msgid ""
"repos:\n"
"  - repo: https://github.com/fsfe/reuse-tool\n"
"    rev: v4.0.2\n"
"    hooks:\n"
"      - id: reuse\n"
msgstr ""
"repos: \n"
"-   repo: https://github.com/fsfe/reuse-tool \n"
"    rev: v1.0.0 \n"
"    hooks: \n"
"    - id: reuse\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: site/content/en/dev.md
msgid ""
"Then run `pre-commit install`. Now, every time you commit, `reuse lint` is "
"run in the background, and will prevent your commit from going through if "
"there was an error."
msgstr ""
"Luego ejecute `pre-commit install`. Ahora, cada vez que escriba, `reuse "
"lint` se ejecuta en segundo plano y evitará que se realice la confirmación "
"si hubo un error."

